<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>인증 코드</title>
    </head>
    <body
        style="
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #e8f0f0;
            font-family: 'Pretendard', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
        "
    >
        <table
            border="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            width="100%"
            style="background-color: #e8f0f0; min-height: 100vh"
        >
            <tr>
                <td align="center" valign="middle" style="padding: 40px 0">
                    <table
                        border="0"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        cellspacing="0"
                        width="600"
                        style="
                            background-color: white;
                            border-radius: 13px;
                            box-shadow: 0px 0px 30px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                            overflow: hidden;
                        "
                    >
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding: 60px 40px">
                                <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px">
                                    <div
                                        style="
                                            color: #333333;
                                            font-size: 28px; /* 44px -> 28px */
                                            font-weight: 700;
                                            line-height: 1.4;
                                        "
                                    >
                                        인증 코드
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px">
                                    <div
                                        style="
                                            display: inline-block;
                                            width: 100%;
                                            max-width: 400px;
                                            background: #ececec;
                                            border-radius: 12px; /* 20px -> 12px */
                                            border: 1px solid #dedede;
                                            padding: 25px 0; /* 높이 대신 padding 사용 */
                                            color: #2c3e50;
                                            font-size: 32px; /* 50px -> 32px */
                                            font-weight: 700;
                                            letter-spacing: 2px;
                                        "
                                    >
                                        <%= verificationCode %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div style="text-align: left">
                                    <p
                                        style="
                                            color: #333333;
                                            font-size: 16px; /* 26px -> 16px */
                                            font-weight: 500;
                                            line-height: 1.6;
                                            margin: 0 0 15px 0; /* 하단 여백 추가 */
                                        "
                                    >
                                        안녕하세요. 연암공과대학교 학우님,
                                    </p>
                                    <p
                                        style="
                                            color: #333333;
                                            font-size: 16px;
                                            font-weight: 500;
                                            line-height: 1.6;
                                            margin: 0 0 30px 0;
                                        "
                                    >
                                        회원가입을 완료하시려면 위의 코드를 입력해 인증을
                                        완료해주세요.<br />
                                        <strong style="color: #e74c3c">(3분 후 만료)</strong>
                                    </p>
                                    <p
                                        style="
                                            color: #999999;
                                            font-size: 14px;
                                            font-weight: 400;
                                            line-height: 1.5;
                                            margin: 0;
                                            border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
                                            padding-top: 20px;
                                        "
                                    >
                                        감사합니다.<br />
                                        연암공과대학교 스터디그룹 매칭 플랫폼
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </body>
</html>
